---

These are unofficial, community-built Model Context Protocol (MCP) servers that
wrap the public APIs of Roshan AI (https://www.roshan-ai.ir). "Roshan", the
Roshan logo, and the product names (Harf, Alefba, Fahm, Baaz, …) are trademarks
of their respective owner and are used here only to identify the upstream
services these tools integrate with. Logos are included from the public
documentation repository (roshan-research/docs) for identification purposes.
